room_title: Escape room "Embassy Escape" by Big Sky Breakout in Missoula
review: Truly a great time for everyone of all ages. I was genuinely surprised at how challenging it was during our "Embassy Escape" and the 1 hour time limit just flew by! Fun, exciting and suspenseful. If you have had any doubts about whether or not to try Big Sky Breakout, don't be shy and go play! You'll be glad you did.
